@{
    ViewBag.Title = "BordersAndBackgrounds";
}

<style type="text/css">
    div
    {
        border: 10px double black;
        background-color: lightgray;
        background-image: url(../../Content/images/triathlon.png);
        background-size: contain;
        background-repeat: repeat;
        background-position: center;
        -moz-background-origin: border-box;
        -webkit-background-origin: border-box;
        background-origin: border-box;
        background-clip: content-box;
    }

    p
    {
        border: medium solid black;
    }

        p:last-child
        {
            border-radius: 55px / 5px; /*horizontal / vertical*/
            border-radius: 55px 20% 5% 10% / 55px 20% 5% 10%; /*horizontal / vertical*/
            padding: 5px;
        }

    #triangle
    {
        border-color: grey transparent transparent transparent;
        border-width: 10px;
        border-style: solid;
        width: 0;
        height: 0;
    }

    textarea
    {
        border: medium solid black;
        background-color: lightgray;
        background-image: url(../../Content/images/triathlon.png);
        -moz-background-size: 60px 60px;
        -o-background-size: 60px 60px;
        -webkit-background-size: 60px 60px;
        background-size: 60px 60px;
        background-repeat: repeat;
        background-attachment: fixed;
        -moz-background-origin: border-box;
        -webkit-background-origin: border-box;
        background-origin: border-box;
    }
</style>

<h2>Borders And Backgrounds</h2>

<div>
    <p>
        There are lots of different kinds of fruit - there are over 500 varieties
of banana alone. By the time we add the countless types of apples, oranges,
and other well-known fruit, we are faced with thousands of choices.
    </p>

    <p>
        There are lots of different kinds of fruit - there are over 500 varieties
of banana alone. By the time we add the countless types of apples, oranges,
and other well-known fruit, we are faced with thousands of choices.
    </p>

    <p>
        <textarea rows="8" cols="30">
        There are lots of different kinds of fruit - there are over 500 varieties
        of banana alone. By the time we add the countless types of apples, oranges,
        and other well-known fruit, we are faced with thousands of choices.
        </textarea>
    </p>
    <div id="triangle"></div>
</div>
